    "## Section 3: Representing functions\n",

    "### Question 1"

  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "source": [
    "from scipy.interpolate import interp1d\n",
    "x_samp = np.arange(0,10)\n",
    "y_samp = np.exp(-x_samp)*x_samp*x_samp"
   ]

   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [

     "data": {

       "<Figure size 432x288 with 1 Axes>"
      ]
     },
     "metadata": {},
     "output_type": "display_data"
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "f_int = interp1d(x_samp,y_samp,kind='cubic')\n",
    "x_plot = np.arange(0,9.1,0.1)\n",
    "plt.plot(x_samp,y_samp,'ro',label='Original data points')\n",
    "plt.plot(x_samp,y_samp,'r-',label='Straight-line fit')\n",
    "plt.plot(x_plot,f_int(x_plot),label='Cubic spline fit')\n",
    "plt.title(\"Fitting a simple function\")\n",
    "plt.xlabel('x')\n",
    "plt.ylabel('y')\n",
    "plt.legend()"

   "source": [

    "## 4. Fourier transforms: basics\n",
    "\n",
    "### Question 1"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 6,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def discrete_ft(y):\n",
    "    \"\"\"Implementation of 1D discrete Fourier transform\"\"\"\n",
    "    leny = len(y)\n",
    "    coeffs = np.zeros(leny,dtype=complex)\n",
    "    for k in range(leny):\n",
    "        for i in range(leny):\n",
    "            coeffs[k] += y[i]*np.exp(-2j*np.pi*k*i/leny)\n",
    "    return coeffs"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "### Question 2"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 7,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "xmax = 2.0\n",
    "nx = 100\n",
    "dx = xmax/nx\n",
    "k = 2*np.pi/xmax\n",
    "x1d = np.arange(0,xmax,dx)\n",
    "simple_sine = np.sin(k*x1d)"
   ]

  {

   "source": [
    "### Question 1"

  {

   "source": [
    "karr = np.zeros(nx)\n",
    "dk = 2*np.pi/xmax\n",
    "nkmax = int(nx/2-1)\n",
    "karr[0:nkmax] = dk*np.arange(0,nx/2-1)\n",
    "karr[nkmax+1:] = dk*np.arange(-nx/2,0)\n",
    "d1_ss_FFT = 1j*karr*ss_FFT\n",
    "diff_simple_sine = np.fft.ifft(d1_ss_FFT)\n",
    "plt.plot(x1d,k*np.cos(k*x1d))\n",

    "### Question 2"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",

   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "100  points with spacing  0.40404040404040403\n",
      "Total charge:  162.08668640471555\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "N = 100\n",
    "xymin = 0\n",
    "xymax = 40\n",
    "delta = (xymax-xymin)/(N-1)\n",
    "print(N,\" points with spacing \",delta)\n",
    "x2 = np.linspace(xymin,xymax,N)\n",
    "y2 = np.linspace(xymin,xymax,N)\n",
    "a2,b2 = np.meshgrid(x2,y2,indexing='ij')\n",
    "dk2d = 2*np.pi/(xymax - xymin)\n",
    "dens_grid = np.sin(dk2d*a2)*np.sin(dk2d*b2)\n",
    "print(\"Total charge: \",delta*delta*np.sum(dens_grid[0:50,0:50]))"
   ]

   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "dg_FFT = np.fft.fftn(dens_grid)\n",
    "nk2dmax = int(N/2-1)\n",
    "k2darr = np.zeros(N)\n",
    "k2darr[0:nk2dmax+1] = dk2d*np.arange(0,N/2)\n",
    "k2darr[nk2dmax+1:] = dk2d*np.arange(-N/2,0)\n",
    "k2d_x, k2d_y = np.meshgrid(k2darr,k2darr)\n",
    "d2_dg_FFT = dg_FFT/(k2d_x*k2d_x + k2d_y*k2d_y+1e-16)\n",
    "d2_dg_FFT[0,0] = 0.0\n",
    "pot = np.fft.ifftn(d2_dg_FFT)"
   ]

   "cell_type": "markdown",

   "source": [
    "### Question 4"
   ]

  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 22,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "N4 = 200\n",
    "xymin4 = 0\n",
    "xymax4 = 80\n",
    "delta4 = (xymax4-xymin4)/(N4-1)\n",
    "x4 = np.linspace(xymin4,xymax4,N4)\n",
    "y4 = np.linspace(xymin4,xymax4,N4)\n",
    "a4,b4 = np.meshgrid(x4,y4,indexing='ij')\n",
    "pot_exact4 = np.zeros((N4,N4))\n",
    "dens_grid4 = np.sin(dk2d*a4+np.pi)*np.sin(dk2d*b4+np.pi)\n",
    "for i, x in enumerate(x4):\n",
    "    for j, y in enumerate(y4):\n",
    "        xw = a4 - x\n",
    "        yw = b4 - y\n",
    "        denom = np.sqrt(xw**2 + yw**2)\n",
    "        denom[i,j] = 1.0\n",
    "        pothere = dens_grid4/denom\n",
    "        pothere[i,j] = 0.0\n",
    "        pot_exact4[i,j] = np.sum(pothere)*delta4*delta4"
   ]
